{
  "description": "A panoramic view of a sprawling city bathed in the warm, golden light of a setting or rising sun. Dark, dramatic clouds hang low in the sky, partially obscuring the sun and creating a sense of atmospheric depth. Below the clouds, the city appears as a patchwork of buildings and streets, with hints of green vegetation intermixed. In the foreground, rolling hills covered in dense trees frame the scene, adding a natural border. The overall impression is one of vastness, with the city stretching out towards the horizon. The light is diffused and soft, casting long shadows and creating a sense of tranquility.",
